{"tid":1306101,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[肥佬黎.jpg] 晤美國國家安全顧問博爾頓 黎智英促請支持鼓勵香港年輕人","createTime":"2019-07-11T04:42:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-10T16:30:38.000Z","uid":54733,"like":44,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"6f3e451a461136bd349214bdfdaa4899e2802b19","tid":1306101,"uid":54733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T04:42:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190711/large/1562805779_4760.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190711%2Flarge%2F1562805779_4760.jpg&h=0f7bdba2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【新增動新聞】正在華盛頓尋求美國政府對香港民主運動支持的香港壹傳媒集團創辦人黎智英，周三與美國國家安全顧問博爾頓(John Bolton)會面，討論有關香港及中國的議題。<br />\n<br />\n黎智英跟博爾頓談及反送中抗爭，懇請他盡量以行動支持香港人，並請求美國政府發表言論支持和鼓勵香港的年輕人。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20190711/59810531\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190711%2F59810531&d=i5E3ds%2FeSPFE00WLmt8522yprV%2B6HEKZLwhfW4p%2FhGU%3D&h=e7f1b6a2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190711%2F59810531&h=6fe5d203\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20190711/59810531</a>"},{"pid":"1232df12697fb1d80204bb2ed59884b29cc45205","tid":1306101,"uid":54733,"like":28,"dislike":0,"score":28,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T04:43:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://x7n5x3t5.stackpathcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/肥佬黎-min.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fx7n5x3t5.stackpathcdn.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F07%2F%E8%82%A5%E4%BD%AC%E9%BB%8E-min.jpg&h=926006e6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"73fe8ffc79715470a04b566c3a2197c67b2f7478","tid":1306101,"uid":1241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T04:43:49.00